OL,3,GNorthern Ireland
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA dry start with sunny spells
OL,6,Fbut cloud will bubble up through the
OL,7,Fmorning with a few showers developing.
OL,8,FThe showers will become heavy and
OL,9,Fthundery in places during the
OL,10,Fafternoon.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FHeavy showers at first but
OL,13,Fthese dying out for a time. Further
OL,14,Fshowers will then spread east
OL,15,Fovernight but the east coast should
OL,16,Fstay mainly dry.
OL,17,
OL,18,CTuesday:FA largely cloudy day with
OL,19,Fbright spells and showers, some of
OL,20,Fthese could be heavy.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
