OL,3,GNorthern Ireland
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Wednesday to Friday:FHeavy
OL,6,Fand thundery showers on Wednesday then
OL,7,Fcloudy with outbreaks of rain
OL,8,Fspreading east on Wednesday. Bright
OL,9,Fand breezy with scattered showers on
OL,10,FFriday.
